articles.title: Russia sends bombers to fly over Belarus, blames EU for migrant catastrophe - Reuters
articles.description: Russia blamed the European Union on Wednesday for the migrant crisis on the border between Belarus and Poland, accusing it of trying to "strangle" Belarus with plans to close part of the frontier and urging it to talk directly with Minsk.
